1. Prošla godinu* nije bila laka. (Last year wasn't easy.)

2. Naredne godine* ćemo učestvovati u još većem broju događaja. (Next year we will participate in even more events.)

3. Planiramo da putujemo u inostranstvo naredne godine*. (We plan to travel abroad next year.)

4. Godinu dana* je prošlo od mog prvog dolaska u Srbiju. (One year has passed since my first arrival to Serbia.)

5. Čitavu godinu* smo se trudili da postignemo rezultate. (We have been trying hard to achieve results throughout the whole year.)